        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I'm the author of Ghostty. If you can outline specifically the features you're looking for, I can make sure they're exposed in some way via the C API. We certainly _support the features_, it's just a question of designing a good C API to expose them. Feel free to join our Discord (https://discord.gg/ghostty) and the `#libghostty` channel we just created where we'll be jamming on API design.\n\nNote for any unfamiliar readers: the API part is new, the core logic part of all this is rock solid and has been part of Ghostty and used by hundreds of thousands of people for years now. ",
